      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Object obj)
        Compares the first and last names of two students and determines if they are equal. If the first names are equal, compare last names: If negative, return -1. If positive, return 1. Equal, return 0. Otherwise, compare first names. If negative, return -1. If positive return 1. Returns -2 if obj is not an instance of the Student class
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface Comparable
